    <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
        <p>{l s='This module My Easy ERP for Prestashop responds effecientely to the problems of logistics and inventory management (stock status) with a complete and powerful ERP solution integrated, easy to configure and cost less.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p>{l s='This module is the result of our many years of experience in logistics and management issues related to e­commerce and in Prestashop technology as we are a certified partner.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p>{l s='Our goal is to provide a module that meets the logistics issues of the largest number of retailers using Prestashop while offering advanced features if necessary.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p>{l s='So you can manage a stock management in a Classic mode or choose the Lean supply chain mode.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p>{l s='In the case of a conventional configuration the module allows you to manage issues reorder automatically in several According to "normal law" (reorder calculated according to the level of risk of rupture), in expert mode or manually forcing My Easy ERP module also allows the automatic creation of replenishment orders from your suppliers, automticly send by email if needed, and their daily management: treatment of receptions, etc.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p>{l s='Configuration of suppliers and products (threshold quantity, delivery time) can be done at the global level, automated or more accurately by supplier and by product.' mod='wic_erp'}</p>
        <p><b>{l s='Finally all the updates of states of stocks are calculated automaticaly in REAL TIME.' mod='wic_erp'}</b></p>
        <p>{l s='This module allows to integrate a full and efficient Embedded ERP in your site Prestashop in few clicks:' mod='wic_erp'}
        <ul>
            <li>{l s='Complete integration into your administration module, click and installation,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='Configure the module simply from your Prestashop Back­Office,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li><b>{l s='Management Mode of stock type Classic with “House In” stock,' mod='wic_erp'}</b></li>
            <li><b>{l s='Mode stock management type Lean supply chain,' mod='wic_erp'}</b></li>
            <li>{l s='Management orders with suppliers,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='Management replenishment level product: control points (quantity from which the command should be launched), safety stock, minimum stock, replenishment lead times by supplier and minimum units per products,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='Mode or expert management under the normal distribution: data calculation based replenishment lead times suppliers and sales statistics over a given period (configurable),' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='Status management commands providers,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='United in stock real­time products and versions: in stock, out of stock, current replenishment,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='States customer orders in real­time commands concerned with products out of stock,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
            <li>{l s='Allows updating customer orders incomplete mass receipt of expected stock,' mod='wic_erp'}</li>
